OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1778505068
OL,3,CPassengers from the hantavirus ship
OL,4,Care back in the UK - but what happens
OL,5,Cnow?
OL,7,FWords by ITV News Producer Jamel Smith
OL,9,FTwenty Brits from the hantavirus-hit
OL,10,Fcruise ship, MV Hondius, have arrived
OL,11,Fback in the UK, where they are
OL,12,Fisolating and being offered practical
OL,13,Fand emotional support.
OL,15,FThree people have so far died,
OL,16,Ffollowing the outbreak on board two
OL,17,Fweeks ago, and multiple others have
OL,18,Fbeen diagnosed with suspected
OL,19,Fhantavirus.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
