FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1778505068
OL,3,CPassengers from the hantavirus ship
OL,4,Care back in the UK - but what happens
OL,5,Cnow?
OL,7,FAfter a flight from Tenerife, the 20
OL,8,FBrits ` alongside one German, who is a
OL,9,FUK resident, and one Japanese
OL,10,Fpassenger ` were taken to Arrowe Park
OL,11,FHospital on the Wirral to quarantine
OL,12,Fon Sunday.
OL,14,FSo what is next for the Brits exposed
OL,15,Fto hantavirus? ITV News explains.
OL,17,FWill they be quarantined?
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1778505068
OL,3,CPassengers from the hantavirus ship
OL,4,Care back in the UK - but what happens
OL,5,Cnow?
OL,7,FYes. The 22 passengers will be housed
OL,8,Fat Arrowe Park Hospital for three
OL,9,Fdays, where they will receive clinical
OL,10,Fassessments and testing by the UK
OL,11,FHealth Security Agency (UKHSA) and NHS
OL,12,Finfectious diseases specialists.
OL,14,FThey will assess whether they can
OL,15,Fsafely isolate at home or in other
OL,16,Faccommodation.
OL,18,FWhat is the quarantine accommodation
OL,19,Flike at Arrowe Park?
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1778505068
OL,3,CPassengers from the hantavirus ship
OL,4,Care back in the UK - but what happens
OL,5,Cnow?
OL,7,FThe site has six storeys of self-
OL,8,Fcontained flats, which come with a
OL,9,Fbedroom, en-suite bathroom, kitchen
OL,10,Fand lounge.
OL,12,FWill this affect normal hospital
OL,13,Fservices at Arrowe Park?
OL,15,FNo. Chief Executive of Wirral
OL,16,FUniversity Teaching Hospital NHS
OL,17,FFoundation Trust Janelle Holmes said
OL,18,Fthere will be "no impact on the
OL,19,Fhospital" and patients should continue
OL,20,Fto attend their appointments as normal.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1778505068
OL,3,CPassengers from the hantavirus ship
OL,4,Care back in the UK - but what happens
OL,5,Cnow?
OL,7,FWhat happens after the initial
OL,8,Fassessment?
OL,10,FThose cleared to isolate at home will
OL,11,Fbe sent away to self-isolate for a
OL,12,Ffurther 42 days.
OL,14,FIf they cannot go home, they will be
OL,15,Fplaced in alternative accommodation.
OL,17,FThey will also all have daily contact
OL,18,Fwith UKHSA health protection teams
OL,19,Fthroughout that period to check on
OL,20,Ftheir well-being and ensure that they
OL,21,Fare supported to isolate safely.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30406
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1778505068
OL,3,CPassengers from the hantavirus ship
OL,4,Care back in the UK - but what happens
OL,5,Cnow?
OL,7,FThe UK government has also ensured
OL,8,Fthat passengers self-isolating are
OL,9,Fgiven the appropriate support.
OL,11,FAre strict measures in place to
OL,12,Fprotect the public while passengers
OL,13,Fare travelling?
OL,15,FYes. The UKHSA said passengers, crew,
OL,16,Fdrivers and medical staff have all
OL,17,Fbeen wearing protective equipment,
OL,18,Fincluding face masks, throughout the
OL,19,Fjourney.
OL,21,FWhat if someone develops symptoms?
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30407
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1778505068
OL,3,CPassengers from the hantavirus ship
OL,4,Care back in the UK - but what happens
OL,5,Cnow?
OL,7,FAny passenger who develops hantavirus
OL,8,Fsymptoms will be sent to Royal
OL,9,FLiverpool University Hospital, which
OL,10,Fhouses the regional Tropical and
OL,11,FInfectious Diseases Unit, Holmes said
OL,13,FWhat about the Japanese passenger?
OL,15,FAt the request of the Japanese
OL,16,Fgovernment, the UK agreed to bring the
OL,17,FJapanese passenger to Arrowe Park,
OL,18,Fwhere they will complete their
OL,19,Fisolation under UKHSA supervision.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
