OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1778505068
OL,3,CPassengers from the hantavirus ship
OL,4,Care back in the UK - but what happens
OL,5,Cnow?
OL,7,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,8,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,9,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,10,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,12,FIs there still a risk to the public?
OL,14,FPublic Health Minister Sharon Hodgson
OL,15,Fsaid the risk remains "extremely low"
OL,16,Fas no passengers are currently showing
OL,17,Fsymptoms and "stringent monitoring
OL,18,Fmeasures" are in place.
OL,20,FAre other countries taking stricter
OL,21,Fmeasures?
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
