FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30409
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1778505068
OL,3,CPassengers from the hantavirus ship
OL,4,Care back in the UK - but what happens
OL,5,Cnow?
OL,7,FGreece has forced a male passenger of
OL,8,Fthe ship to spend 45 days in mandatory
OL,9,Fhospital quarantine in Athens.
OL,11,FHe will be placed in a specially
OL,12,Fprepared negative-pressure isolation
OL,13,Fchamber at Attikon University Hospital
OL,14,F- a sealed space designed to prevent
OL,15,Fcontaminants from escaping.
OL,17,FIn Spain, 14 passengers will be placed
OL,18,Fin biosafety isolation beds at the
OL,19,FGomez Ulla military hospital in Madrid.
OL,26,@{D@Brw
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/11
