OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1778505068
OL,3,CPassengers from the hantavirus ship
OL,4,Care back in the UK - but what happens
OL,5,Cnow?
OL,7,FWhy is the WHO recommending 42 days of
OL,8,Fquarantine?
OL,10,FWHO says the 42-day period is a
OL,11,Fprecautionary measure, based on
OL,12,Fevidence from past outbreaks of Andes
OL,13,Fvirus, a strain of hantavirus, and
OL,14,Fthat the infection is most contagious
OL,15,Fin the early stages of illness.
OL,17,FAlso, it is possible that someone can
OL,18,Fpass on the virus before they
OL,19,Fexperience symptoms, known as pre-
OL,20,Fsymptomatic transmission.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
